  Description: Dwarves have a well-earned reputation as a stoic and stern people,
    but they also have an unbridled zeal and deeply value artisanship. To a stranger,
    they can seem untrusting and clannish, but to their friends and family, they
    are warm and caring. While trust from a dwarf is hard-won, once gained it is
    as strong as iron.
